  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the analgesic efficacy of perineural fentanyl
      combined with local anesthetics in the post operative pain control with continuous femoral
      nerve block after total knee arthroplasty.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
